<h2 id="chord-progressions">Chord progressions</h2>

<p>Big picture, the song has two progressions and they look like this. For every letter below AND for each â€œ/â€, youâ€™re playing four counts (one measure) of that chord. The â€œ/â€ character below means that you should stay on the prior chord for one additional measure.</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Verse     D   /   G   D   /   /   /   A
          D   /   G   D   G   D   A   D

Chorus    D   /   G   D   G   D   D   A
          D   /   G   D   G   D   A   D
</code></pre></div></div>

